#

Bean and Cheese Burrito

15 min
$5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickComfort FoodAmerican-Mexican

Description

A hearty and satisfying burrito filled with creamy cheese and savory beans, wrapped in a warm tortilla.

Ingredients

  • flour tortillas: 2 large
  • refried beans: 1 cup
  • shredded cheese (cheddar or monterey jack): 1 cup
  • sour cream: 1/4 cup
  • salsa: 1/4 cup
  • chopped green onions: 2 tablespoons
